text: Michel Kiesgen (born 15 September 1933) is a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Luxembourg City
